subtitle: the 29th day of the Omer I said of Hud
loving kindness and humility
examine the love in your humility
healthy humility is not demoralizing it
brings love and joy not fear
humility that lacks love has to be
re-examined for its authenticity
sometimes humility can be confused with
low self-esteem which would cause it to
be unloving humility brings love because
it gives you the ability to rise above
yourself and love another arrogance in
the guise of Love Means loving yourself
or even worse making others apart and an
extension of yourself and yourself love
ask yourself
does your humility cause you to be more
loving or giving or does it inhibit and
constrain you do you feel humble and
happy or humble and miserable
exercise for today
before praying with humility and
acknowledgment of God give some charity
it will enhance your prayer guaranteed
